<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
  <title>Application Submitted - Mazaryn</title>
  <link phx-track-static rel="stylesheet" href={~p"/assets/app.css"}/>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      background: #27282e;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#27282e]">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-[#27282e] flex items-center justify-center p-8">
    <div class="max-w-2xl w-full">
      <div class="bg-[#323340] rounded-[20px] shadow-2xl p-12 text-center">

        <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-green-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-white text-3xl font-bold font-['Poppins'] mb-4">
          Application Submitted Successfully!
        </h1>

        <p class="text-[#c5c7c8] text-lg font-['Poppins'] mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Thank you for applying to become an artist on Mazaryn. Your application has been received and is now under review by our admin team.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-[#3a3b4a] rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-white text-xl font-semibold font-['Poppins'] mb-4">
            What happens next?
          </h2>

          <div class="space-y-4 text-left">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                <span class="text-blue-500 text-sm font-bold">1</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-white text-base font-semibold font-['Poppins']">Review Process</h3>
                <p class="text-[#c5c7c8] text-sm font-['Poppins']">
                  Our team will carefully review your application, experience, and proof links.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                <span class="text-blue-500 text-sm font-bold">2</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-white text-base font-semibold font-['Poppins']">Decision</h3>
                <p class="text-[#c5c7c8] text-sm font-['Poppins']">
                  You'll receive a notification once your application has been reviewed (typically within 2-3 business days).
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                <span class="text-blue-500 text-sm font-bold">3</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-white text-base font-semibold font-['Poppins']">Get Started</h3>
                <p class="text-[#c5c7c8] text-sm font-['Poppins']">
                  Once approved, you'll be able to upload and share your music with the Mazaryn community!
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href={"/" <> @locale <> "/music"}
            class="px-8 py-3 bg-blue-500 rounded-lg text-white text-base font-semibold font-['Poppins'] hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors"
          >
            Explore Music
          </a>

          <a
            href={"/" <> @locale <> "/home"}
            class="px-8 py-3 bg-[#3a3b4a] rounded-lg text-white text-base font-semibold font-['Poppins'] hover:bg-[#404152] transition-colors"
          >
            Back to Home
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-gray-600">
          <p class="text-[#aaaaaa] text-sm font-['Poppins']">
            Questions? Contact us at
            <a href="mailto:support@mazaryn.com" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-400">
              support@mazaryn.com
            </a>
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
